snippet.title: 3D Pixel Art Game Project (1st Trailer)
snippet.description:
I am a high-school student and I have been working for some time on a game. 

The whole purpose of this trailer is to get feedback about the direction I followed in this new concept of 3D Pixel Art. Therefore, feel free to comment below (however harsh it might be). 

Subscribe if you want to follow this game's progress (which doesn't have a name yet)
